{"tid":1321234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我懷疑好多廢老支持香港同中國政府係因為WhatsApp 同 Facebook","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:11:28.000Z","uid":112551,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66c4d016f9aadefc284ba1e7c504f0dabd5209d0","tid":1321234,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"我屋企兩老全部都係黃絲，一個小學grad 一個中六grad，基本佢地日日唱雙簧屌7政府支持學生。<br />\n我比較少發表意見，但佢都知我係黃。<br />\n佢兩個最奇怪既係唔識電腦同用Nokia舊手機，斷絕 WhatsApp同Facebook，佢地都睇CCTVB 有線 東方 同蘋果。<br />\n一直追開連登都見到啲父母都係藍屍，但我個兩個唔係，我一直諗點解啦，明明都睇CCTVB 東方。<br />\n但我依家發現WhatsApp Facebook 先係最萬惡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為啲廢老唔識分Fake news，CCTVB只可以話偏頗但未去到Fake news，Fake news先真正去到洗腦的層次。<br />\n<br />\n好多廢老都識用智能手機用社交軟件，基本上有如暴露在輻射之下，腦細胞突變晒，變成愛國的僵屍，仇恨外國的一切。<br />\n<br />\nWell⋯⋯只係我個人猜測，因為我身邊人親戚都非藍屍，我都唔知點解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我媽識啲新移民都係反共。"},{"pid":"ebd53d7b6315f3c32df660ee51c03c3c8e8fb762","tid":1321234,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:21:33.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f6b93494ee8d72d97bae4adc5dac553f21d7edfd","tid":1321234,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"然後呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da765d47237408fe2cf01540092d7e824b77fcaa","tid":1321234,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"221c6774267be93e8b8a2686d1f543466c2a97ac","tid":1321234,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:24:23.000Z","msg":"Facebook 你睇到d reply /topic全部由 朱西八格決定，你冇權選擇，極度邪惡"},{"pid":"58638a5744d866fe675d187cc85aa8b35f149bc4","tid":1321234,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6b93494ee8d72d97bae4adc5dac553f21d7edfd","tid":1321234,"u